<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="124" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="1.[812,1451,1184,1304]" pageId="1" pageNumber="124">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[813,923,1185,1209]" pageId="1" pageNumber="124">Remarks.</emphasis>
This is species is distinct in having unique elytral maculations (unicolored or with simple spots in the elytra of the other species of this genus) and anchor-shaped ventral projection.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="124" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="1.[813,1452,1344,1432]" pageId="1" pageNumber="124">
